the plot the relative rate of change anywhere in the timeline, which allows comparison of one plot with the others throughout the pandemic.\n\n{{Graph:Chart\n|type=line\n|linewidth=1\n|showSymbols=1\n|width=800\n|height=400<!--height = 80 X <no. of log10 cycles in y axis>-->\n|colors=#FF6347,#FF8C00,#FFC000,#87CEEB,#343132\n|showValues=\n|xAxisTitle=Date\n|xType = date\n|xAxisAngle=-40\n|x=26 Feb, 27 Feb, 28 Feb, 29 Feb, 1 Mar, 2 Mar, 3 Mar, 4 Mar, 5 Mar, 6 Mar, 7 Mar, 8 Mar, 9 Mar, 10 Mar, 11 Mar, 12 Mar, 13 Mar, 14 Mar, 15 Mar, 16 Mar, 17 Mar, 18 Mar, 19 Mar, 20 Mar, 21 Mar, 22 Mar, 23 Mar, 24 Mar, 25 Mar, 26 Mar, 27 Mar, 28 Mar, 29 Mar, 30 Mar, 31 Mar, 1 Apr, 2 Apr, 3 Apr, 4 Apr, 5 Apr, 6 Apr, 7 Apr, 8 Apr, 9 Apr, 10 Apr, 11 Apr, 12 Apr, 13 Apr, 14 Apr, 15 Apr, 16 Apr, 17 Apr, 18 Apr, 19 Apr, 20 Apr, 21 Apr, 22 Apr, 23 Apr, 24 Apr, 25 Apr, 26 Apr, 27 Apr, 28 Apr, 29 Apr, 30 Apr, 1 May, 2 May\n|yAxisTitle=No. of cases\n|legend=Legend\n|y1= 2, 2, 2, 4, 4, 4, 5, 5, 6, 6, 6, 7, 16, 19, 20, 21, 28, 31, 53, 187, 241, 302, 461, 495, 646, 784, 887, 991, 1057, 1197, 1408, 1526, 1625, 1865, 2039, 2291, 2450, 2640, 2818, 3062, 3556, 4005, 4207, 4489, 4695, 5011, 5230, 5496, 5837, 6383, 6919, 7025, 7638, 8348, 8418, 9565, 10076, 11057, 11983, 12723, 13328, 13915, 14612, 15525, 16817, 18114, 19103\n|y1Title=Total Confirmed cases\n|y2=2, 2, 2, 4, 4, 4, 5, 5, 6, 5, 5, 6, 15, 18, 18, 19, 25, 28, 50, 183, 237, 295, 454, 487, 638, 773, 875, 966, 1016, 1165, 1371, 1485, 1575, 1782, 1931, 2153, 2289, 2478, 2646, 2847, 3246, 3521, 3679, 3854, 3902, 4163, 4111, 4279, 4363, 4826, 5146, 5125, 5662, 6312, 6272, 7291, 7708, 8485, 8932, 9588, 10018, 10594, 11067, 11757, 12117, 12982, 13864\n|y2Title=Total Active cases\n|y3= 2, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 9, 3, 1, 1, 7, 3, 22, 134, 54, 61, 159, 34, 151, 138, 103, 104, 66, 140, 211, 118, 99, 240, 174, 252, 159, 190, 178, 244, 494, 449, 202, 282, 206, 316, 219, 266, 341, 546, 536, 106, 613, 710, 70, 1147, 511, 981, 881, 783, 605, 587, 69